Package: r4subusability
Title: Usability Indicators for Clinical Submission Readiness
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Pawan Rama", "Mali", email = "prm@outlook.in",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7864-5819"))
Description: Quantifies reviewer-experience and usability indicators for
    clinical regulatory submissions. Assesses variable label quality,
    Define-XML (Extensible Markup Language) completeness, dataset
    annotation coverage, and reviewer guide presence. Emits standardised
    R4SUB (R for Regulatory Submission) evidence table rows via
    'r4subcore' for integration with 'r4subscore' and 'r4subprofile'.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/R4SUB/r4subusability
BugReports: https://github.com/R4SUB/r4subusability/issues
